Merkel Says Euro States Won’t Make Crisis Decisions Today

-- B y   J a m e s   G .   N e u g e r
-- 
2011-10-23T07:26:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/merkel-says-euro-states-won-t-make-crisis-decisions-today.html
German  Chancellor Angela Merkel  said
euro-area leaders won’t make final decisions at a summit today
on the debt crisis. She told reporters in Brussels before the
meeting that there will be “focused, important discussions.”
Another summit is scheduled for Oct. 26.  To contact the reporter on this story:
